data.name: Panel_ControlOverlay_Label.Text
data.value:
This window is the command center of LJTD.
Here you control your objective and a Flash timer as well
It's actually the overlay you will see in your game. Therefor the slides on the left side will help to improve the usability in-game.

data.name: Panel_Minimap_Label.Text
data.value:
This window is an overlay for the in-game minimap.
It's used to show additional information like durations of respawning objectives or ping symbol when an objective is close to it's spawn time. You can also use the Wardmap feature to create infitive wards with it.

data.name: Panel_Settings_Label.Text
data.value:
This settings let you customize over 100 of different things for your LJTD.
These tabs are for seperating features into groups:
- Main - Visual - Chat - Hotkey - Color - Minimap - Macros
You are missing a feature or just want to suggest one. Therefore use our .
